<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span><span style="color:#008000">(١٢٦٨ - ١٣٣٢ هـ)</span> <span style="color:#008000">(١٨٥٢ - ١٩١٤ م)</span><a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
